[this is what I ate most of the time.]

44
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:42,190
[I kept complaining about it.]

45
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:45,960
[But after that incident,]

46
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:49,010
[I never got the chance
to complain anymore.]

47
