[Death Notice, Xu Wei Yi]

65
00:06:36,510 --> 00:06:38,750
[That was the coldest moment in my life.]

66
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:41,090
[I even thought of giving up.]

67
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,290
[But]

68
00:06:44,020 --> 00:06:45,900
[a weird passer-by appeared.]

69
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:48,200
[She was like the sun,]

70
00:06:48,670 --> 00:06:50,390
[giving me warmth in the freezing cold.]

71
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:54,400
[I believe that my dad was framed.]

72
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:56,120
[Someone stole his hard work]

73
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:57,720
[and forced him into a dead end.]

74
00:06:58,840 --> 00:06:59,770
[I swore]

75
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:02,240
[to make sure the thief got punished.]

76
00:07:03,340 --> 00:07:04,800
[I want to clear my dad's name.]

77
00:07:09,310 --> 00:07:11,300
So your dad's program was really powerful.

78
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,690
During the financial crisis,

79
00:07:12,850 --> 00:07:14,830
a lot of companies
survived with my dad's program

80
00:07:15,390 --> 00:07:17,200
and became corporate later on.

81
00:07:17,790 --> 00:07:20,200
The company that framed
my dad for plagiarism

82
