and started a lot of new companies.

85
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:32,900
So the original developer
became a thief.

86
00:07:33,300 --> 00:07:34,650
He had to bear
a bad reputation for no reason.

87
00:07:34,780 --> 00:07:35,900
And the thief

88
00:07:35,980 --> 00:07:37,580
became prosperous

89
00:07:37,659 --> 00:07:39,180
with stolen fame and fortune.

90
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,710
Does that make sense?

91
00:07:40,790 --> 00:07:41,630
It doesn't.

92
00:07:42,710 --> 00:07:43,470
But honestly,

93
00:07:43,550 --> 00:07:44,750
you're really capable in my eyes.

94
00:07:44,830 --> 00:07:45,710
In my heart,

95
00:07:45,790 --> 00:07:46,710
you can take down

96
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:48,840
any problem that comes your way.

97
00:07:48,950 --> 00:07:50,080
I'm not that capable.

98
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:51,200
You on the other hand,

99
00:07:51,280 --> 00:07:52,810
are exactly the same as

100
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:54,350
the woman I met.

101
00:07:59,640 --> 00:08:00,850
What do you mean exactly the same?

102
00:08:01,790 --> 00:08:02,970
[You're both my sun.]

103
00:08:06,190 --> 00:08:07,590
Not as beautiful,

104
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,760
but same because you're simple-minded.

105
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:11,500
You don't think before you act.

106
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:13,520
Say that again?

107
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:16,630
She called herself an old, aunt fairy.

108
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:17,570
What?

109
00:08:17,660 --> 00:08:18,540
Old, aunt fairy.

110
00:08:22,929 --> 00:08:23,820
I'll eat my noodles.

111
00:08:30,159 --> 00:08:31,520
You're really not going back?

112
00:08:31,850 --> 00:08:33,110
It's raining outside.

113
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:34,570
I can't go back.

114
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:44,680
♫ You're everywhere ♫

115
00:08:46,910 --> 00:08:49,150
♫ You should be a character ♫

116
00:08:49,340 --> 00:08:53,140
♫ In a story ♫

117
00:08:55,150 --> 00:08:58,790
♫ You have an obvious love
for sunny days ♫

118
00:08:58,870 --> 00:09:02,070
♫ And a sunny person like you ♫

119
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:09,050
♫ Will expose my love to the world ♫

120
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:13,920
Mr. Wei,

121
00:09:14,010 --> 00:09:15,370
the Family First app

122
00:09:15,450 --> 00:09:16,690
that we wanted to launch with a bang

123
00:09:16,770 --> 00:09:19,210
has some tough issues in the system.

124
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:21,570
It's highly possible that
we can't launch it in time.

125
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:24,240
If the Family First app
can't go online as planned,

126
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,840
we won't be able to uphold the

127
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:28,240
gambling agreement with our investors.

128
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:31,440
I won't give up on this project.

129
00:09:31,890 --> 00:09:32,890
If people are the problem,

130
00:09:33,020 --> 00:09:33,950
get someone else.

131
00:09:34,350 --> 00:09:35,150
Yes, sir.

132
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,000
I understand.

133
00:09:43,090 --> 00:09:45,290
[Summer Time]

134
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,210
The sun is great.

135
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,320
Please shine on me more more.

136
00:10:05,730 --> 00:10:07,750
I haven't been in the sun
like this for a long time.

137
00:10:10,760 --> 00:10:11,570
Mr. Wei,

138
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:12,800
Miss Qin Yue heard that

139
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:14,240
you're in the office a lot

140
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,330
and she insists on coming over.

141
00:10:15,560 --> 00:10:16,840
I said you won't have time to see her,

142
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:18,140
but she insisted.

143
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:21,050
He couldn't stop me.

144
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:27,380
Xuan He,

145
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:30,020
aunty called me just now.

146
00:10:30,140 --> 00:10:32,030
She said someone is moving into the

147
00:10:32,110 --> 00:10:33,350
wedding home that's been empty
for ten years.

148
00:10:33,500 --> 00:10:34,460
What's going on?

149
00:10:35,230 --> 00:10:36,710
It's exactly what it means.

150
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,960
Is Lei Chu Xia moving in?

151
00:10:41,070 --> 00:10:43,350
You gave her the keys
to the home from ten years ago?

152
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:45,310
Are you getting back together?

153
00:10:45,760 --> 00:10:48,220
That home was prepared for her.

154
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:49,260
Xuan He,

155
00:10:49,340 --> 00:10:51,200
have you ever cared about my feelings?

156
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:52,930
She disappeared for ten years.

157
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,980
She doesn't remember you anymore.

158
00:10:55,060 --> 00:10:56,620
She has a new life now.

159
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,510
Your relationship

160
00:10:58,880 --> 00:11:00,880
is lost in time and will not return.

161
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,520
Are you still holding on?

162
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:06,010
This has nothing to do with you.

163
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:09,260
Nothing to do with me?

164
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:11,860
Wei Xuan He,

165
00:11:11,940 --> 00:11:13,300
I've been serious since

166
00:11:13,380 --> 00:11:14,580
the first second we've been together.

167
00:11:14,760 --> 00:11:16,100
But now I know

168
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,800
you don't think the same way.

169
00:11:18,060 --> 00:11:19,780
I was worried that you'd be tired with work

170
00:11:19,860 --> 00:11:21,180
and made some chicken soup for you.

171
00:11:22,330 --> 00:11:24,180
I look so pathetic now.

172
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:33,440
You can throw it out.

173
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:21,170
Aren't you Qin Yue?

174
00:12:21,250 --> 00:12:22,840
I'm your die hard fan.

175
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:23,520
Hello.

176
00:12:23,630 --> 00:12:25,190
Can I take a picture with you?

177
00:12:25,800 --> 00:12:27,250
I'm sorry I have something on.

178
00:12:28,560 --> 00:12:30,240
I gave you a lot of coins,

179
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:32,190
but you won't even take a picture with me?

180
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:33,970
Are you looking down on me?

181
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:36,130
I'm going to get a picture anyway.
Get over here.

182
00:12:50,910 --> 00:12:51,730
Stop filming.

183
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:53,230
He hit me!

184
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:54,320
-Are you alright?
-I'm fine.

185
00:12:54,400 --> 00:12:54,960
Cheat.

186
00:12:55,640 --> 00:12:56,520
You want this to be personal or official?

187
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:58,600
Streamer Qin Yue cheating her fans.

188
00:13:10,660 --> 00:13:14,740
♫ When we connect, your eyes shine ♫

189
00:13:15,790 --> 00:13:19,120
♫ Is there something to be said? ♫

190
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:20,200
[Xuan He,]

191
00:13:21,070 --> 00:13:23,630
[Lei Chu Xia was once your sun.]

192
00:13:24,880 --> 00:13:27,790
[One day, I'll become your sun.]

193
00:13:31,450 --> 00:13:33,490
♫ We need not be together ♫

194
00:13:33,490 --> 00:13:36,850
♫ When we're in love ♫

195
00:13:36,850 --> 00:13:38,890
♫ Why should we hurt each other ♫

196
00:13:38,890 --> 00:13:42,170
♫ If there is no future between us? ♫

197
00:13:42,330 --> 00:13:46,230
♫ No matter how hard we try ♫

198
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:50,040
♫ Our love would be defeated by a thorn ♫

199
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:55,360
♫ I should give myself a chance ♫

200
00:13:55,890 --> 00:14:01,610
♫ I love you in a different way ♫

201
00:14:01,690 --> 00:14:06,150
♫ I wish you happiness
until the end of time ♫

202
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:10,960
Mr. Wei.

203
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:12,990
You've been standing all night.

204
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:14,730
Mr. Wei Sr just won't see you.

205
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:16,490
Why don't you go home first?

206
00:14:22,630 --> 00:14:23,470
Mr. Wei.

207
00:14:26,670 --> 00:14:27,490
Dad.

208
00:14:32,050 --> 00:14:33,950
Have you cleared your mind
after standing for a night?

209
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:36,790
You got into the top story

210
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:39,270
for the sake of a woman.

211
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:41,300
Aren't you ashamed?

212
00:14:42,500 --> 00:14:43,730
She's a girl

213
00:14:44,580 --> 00:14:46,060
and a streamer contracted to us.

214
00:14:46,880 --> 00:14:48,050
I can't just sit around

215
00:14:48,630 --> 00:14:49,650
when she's bullied.

216
00:14:49,730 --> 00:14:51,690
I'm not only talking about this incident.

217
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:53,410
Is you company

218
00:14:53,640 --> 00:14:54,890
still trying to get listed?

219
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:58,400
You're not working on
the company's program.

220
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:01,880
Not solving the issue with

221
00:15:01,960 --> 00:15:03,280
the Family First app.

222
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:06,370
But instead you're caught up
in issues with women.

223
00:15:07,570 --> 00:15:10,050
Are you worthy of the Wei family name?

224
00:15:12,640 --> 00:15:13,520
I'm working on it.

225
00:15:14,280 --> 00:15:15,130
Working...

226
00:15:16,570 --> 00:15:17,940
This is something that the Wei family

227
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:21,120
should never say.

228
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:23,490
If you can't solve
the problem in the company,

229
00:15:23,880 --> 00:15:25,220
never see me again.

230
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:18,840
I don't think you did anything wrong.

231
00:16:19,740 --> 00:16:20,540
So,

232
00:16:20,620 --> 00:16:21,540
you should stand firm

233
00:16:21,620 --> 00:16:22,780
on your ground.

234
00:16:23,050 --> 00:16:24,450
Don't change yourself to fit

235
00:16:24,530 --> 00:16:26,170
the mould that people make for you.

236
00:17:43,980 --> 00:17:44,820
Hello, sir.

237
00:17:44,900 --> 00:17:46,020
Please present your ID.

238
00:17:59,690 --> 00:18:06,450
[Yao Yang Tech, Zhou Sui]

239
00:18:10,610 --> 00:18:12,210
Are you here on behalf of Zhou Sui?

240
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:13,370
Yes.

241
00:18:24,600 --> 00:18:26,350
It's normal to be nervous
the first time you're here.

242
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:27,420
Relax.

243
00:18:28,720 --> 00:18:29,780
Here, take a seat.

244
00:18:37,080 --> 00:18:38,270
Catch up to the rhythm

245
00:18:38,760 --> 00:18:40,440
and copy the source code.

246
00:18:43,850 --> 00:18:45,150
This isn't from our company?

247
00:18:47,420 --> 00:18:48,780
Why would we copy it

248
00:18:48,860 --> 00:18:49,930
if it's from our company?

249
00:18:50,500 --> 00:18:51,660
Zhou Sui told me

250
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:53,270
that you are highly skilled.

251
00:18:54,790 --> 00:18:56,430
But why do you seem a little slow?

252
00:19:00,420 --> 00:19:01,530
Isn't this stealing?

253
00:19:03,640 --> 00:19:04,620
Reference.

254
00:19:05,320 --> 00:19:06,780
Standing on the shoulder of others

255
00:19:07,040 --> 00:19:08,350
to improve yourself.

256
00:19:09,950 --> 00:19:11,000
President Zhao said that.

257
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:12,320
But I totally agree.

258
00:19:14,120 --> 00:19:14,960
Zhao Yao Yang?

259
00:19:15,360 --> 00:19:16,070
Yes.

260
00:19:16,320 --> 00:19:18,720
President Zhao takes this project
very seriously.

261
00:19:19,120 --> 00:19:19,920
Furthermore,

262
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:22,100
he would come over and check.

263
00:19:22,940 --> 00:19:25,350
Work hard if you want a promotion.

264
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:28,800
Mr. Zhao, you're here.

265
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:42,320
Mr. Zhao.

266
00:19:43,320 --> 00:19:44,330
How's the progress?

267
00:19:44,720 --> 00:19:46,330
I've split them into two groups,

268
00:19:46,440 --> 00:19:48,420
one will collect information,

269
00:19:48,500 --> 00:19:50,900
the other will simultaneously
consolidate the content.

270
00:19:51,360 --> 00:19:53,390
We'll 100% be able to launch in time.

271
00:19:54,400 --> 00:19:55,350
It needs to be faster.

272
00:19:55,850 --> 00:19:57,520
This smart method

273
00:19:57,600 --> 00:19:59,170
is copied by a lot of other companies.

274
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:06,400
There's only one way for us to win.

275
00:20:07,040 --> 00:20:08,870
And that's stealing faster than others.

276
00:20:16,720 --> 00:20:17,830
Okay, get back to work.

277
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:18,770
Yes, sir.

278
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:21,020
Take care, Mr. Zhao.

279
00:20:23,880 --> 00:20:24,930
