I don't know what you're talking about.

567
00:35:39,980 --> 00:35:41,100
Stop pretending.

568
00:35:42,560 --> 00:35:43,720
Why would you do that?

569
00:35:44,570 --> 00:35:46,570
Would you be able to bear the
responsibility of taking a human life?

570
00:35:50,060 --> 00:35:51,040
Human life?

571
00:35:53,600 --> 00:35:54,920
Does she count as human?

572
00:35:55,420 --> 00:35:56,370
What are you talking about?

573
00:35:56,520 --> 00:35:57,480
Say that again.

574
00:35:58,230 --> 00:35:59,110
Say that again!

575
00:35:59,190 --> 00:35:59,870
Xiao Dong.

576
00:36:00,680 --> 00:36:01,600
Listen.

577
00:36:01,820 --> 00:36:02,930
He's my student.

578
00:36:03,200 --> 00:36:04,300
Let me handle this.

579
00:36:04,760 --> 00:36:06,260
I'll give you an explanation.

580
00:36:08,590 --> 00:36:11,150
Go take care of Chu Xia.

581
00:36:40,590 --> 00:36:41,610
Wang Yi Xin.

582
00:36:44,400 --> 00:36:46,210
You're my top student.

583
00:36:47,720 --> 00:36:48,930
But this time,

584
00:36:49,680 --> 00:36:51,160
you've gone too far.

585
00:36:53,200 --> 00:36:54,030
Why?

586
00:36:54,440 --> 00:36:55,250
Professor.

587
00:36:56,960 --> 00:37:00,170
We can harness the energy of the universe

588
00:37:01,160 --> 00:37:06,620
and travel from past to future.

589
00:37:08,790 --> 00:37:10,450
That's such a wonderful thing.

590
00:37:11,080 --> 00:37:12,440
If we can

591
00:37:13,980 --> 00:37:15,250
find out

592
00:37:16,340 --> 00:37:18,650
the truth about her time-travelling,

593
00:37:19,490 --> 00:37:21,650
it'll be an outstanding step

594
00:37:23,130 --> 00:37:25,890
in the history of science.

595
00:37:26,520 --> 00:37:27,690
Aren't you tempted?

596
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:29,260
I am.

597
00:37:29,960 --> 00:37:31,000
Of course I'm tempted.

598
00:37:32,830 --> 00:37:36,600
Should I murder you now then?

599
00:37:37,350 --> 00:37:39,500
All the achievement and honour

600
00:37:39,960 --> 00:37:41,000
of researching Chu Xia

601
00:37:41,790 --> 00:37:43,000
would be mine then.

602
00:37:44,190 --> 00:37:45,110
Right?

603
00:37:45,460 --> 00:37:46,580
Should I kill you?

604
00:37:46,940 --> 00:37:48,850
How is what you're doing now

605
00:37:49,380 --> 00:37:50,740
different from murder?

606
00:37:52,600 --> 00:37:53,530
Firstly,

607
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:56,170
I didn't commit murder.

608
00:37:57,580 --> 00:37:58,640
Secondly,

609
00:38:01,230 --> 00:38:02,570
is there energy to be

610
00:38:03,490 --> 00:38:05,210
taken from humans?

611
00:38:05,970 --> 00:38:07,670
I just did what I needed to do.

612
00:38:09,180 --> 00:38:10,400
I just didn't expect

613
00:38:10,550 --> 00:38:13,360
taking such a small amount of energy

614
00:38:13,700 --> 00:38:15,100
would cause her to black out.

615
00:38:15,210 --> 00:38:16,810
You know well that Chu Xia

616
00:38:16,890 --> 00:38:18,400
will disappear if she runs out of energy.

617
00:38:18,840 --> 00:38:20,180
If you take her energy,

618
00:38:20,260 --> 00:38:21,920
it's the same as committing murder.

619
00:38:22,420 --> 00:38:23,990
Where do you draw the line?

620
00:38:24,470 --> 00:38:25,350
The line?

621
00:38:26,350 --> 00:38:27,380
Professor Chen,

622
00:38:27,650 --> 00:38:29,340
you were the one who told us

623
00:38:29,430 --> 00:38:32,760
that science is crossing the line,
one step at a time!

624
00:38:32,960 --> 00:38:35,810
Just because we cross the line
doesn't mean there's no line!

625
00:38:38,280 --> 00:38:39,710
I also told you

626
00:38:40,890 --> 00:38:44,100
that science is for
bringing happiness to people.

627
00:38:44,960 --> 00:38:46,410
Not to bring harm.

628
00:38:48,770 --> 00:38:49,760
Wang Yi Xin,

629
00:38:50,950 --> 00:38:52,420
I'm giving you one last chance.

630
00:38:53,360 --> 00:38:54,940
Stop everything you're doing

631
00:38:55,690 --> 00:38:58,370
and apologise to Xiao Dong and Chu Xia.

632
00:38:59,630 --> 00:39:00,990
Everything that I have done

633
00:39:03,610 --> 00:39:05,450
is for the advancement of mankind.

634
00:39:07,800 --> 00:39:08,800
I didn't do wrong.

635
00:39:21,960 --> 00:39:22,940
No,

636
00:39:25,350 --> 00:39:26,460
you didn't do wrong.

637
00:39:28,480 --> 00:39:29,980
I'm the one who's wrong.

638
00:39:30,060 --> 00:39:31,190
Terribly wrong.

639
00:39:32,520 --> 00:39:33,830
I've underestimated you.

640
00:39:36,530 --> 00:39:37,900
You have big ambitions.

641
00:39:38,500 --> 00:39:39,820
415

642
00:39:40,420 --> 00:39:42,530
won't be able to contain you anymore.

643
00:39:46,560 --> 00:39:47,720
[Wang Yi Xin]

644
00:39:49,130 --> 00:39:50,350
Pack your things

645
00:39:50,720 --> 00:39:51,790
and get out!

646
00:40:02,840 --> 00:40:04,440
Stand still. Don't move.

647
00:40:10,280 --> 00:40:12,080
Let me tell you, Jin Xiao Rui,

648
00:40:12,550 --> 00:40:14,030
I'm asking you one last time.

649
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:17,890
Do you know it or not?

650
00:40:18,540 --> 00:40:20,500
Yuan Yuan, I really don't know.

651
00:40:20,760 --> 00:40:21,560
Don't know?

652
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:28,380
Say that again

653
00:40:28,520 --> 00:40:29,840
and I'll give you clips.

654
00:40:30,640 --> 00:40:31,640
More clips.

655
00:40:31,720 --> 00:40:32,560
You decide what to do.

656
00:40:32,640 --> 00:40:33,520
Are you going to tell?

657
00:40:33,680 --> 00:40:35,640
Xiao Dong really didn't tell me anything.

658
00:40:35,720 --> 00:40:37,320
I don't know anything about Chu Xia.

659
00:40:37,400 --> 00:40:38,960
Do you think I'm blind?

660
00:40:39,120 --> 00:40:40,320
I saw very clearly

661
00:40:40,410 --> 00:40:42,330
how Chu Xia was in the afternoon.

662
00:40:42,410 --> 00:40:43,750
Xu Xiao Dong came
and carried her off straight away.

663
00:40:43,830 --> 00:40:45,730
I'm not going to believe
he doesn't know anything.

664
00:40:45,830 --> 00:40:48,110
It's even harder to believe
that he knew something

665
00:40:49,000 --> 00:40:50,600
and didn't tell you.

666
00:40:50,680 --> 00:40:52,320
I'm no longer best friend with Xiao Dong.

667
00:40:52,320 --> 00:40:53,880
Why would he tell me anything?

668
00:40:53,960 --> 00:40:55,010
Are you going to tell the truth?

669
00:40:55,440 --> 00:40:56,340
I don't know.

670
00:40:56,520 --> 00:40:57,320
Xiao Rui.

671
00:40:58,000 --> 00:40:59,040
What are you...

672
00:40:59,120 --> 00:40:59,840
Xiao Dong.

673
00:41:00,440 --> 00:41:01,600
You're finally back!

674
00:41:01,840 --> 00:41:02,520
Chu Xia.

675
00:41:02,600 --> 00:41:03,760
Look at my face and hands.

676
00:41:03,840 --> 00:41:04,480
Are you all right?

677
00:41:05,480 --> 00:41:06,940
I'm fine, don't worry about me.

678
00:41:07,020 --> 00:41:08,630
Why did you faint?

679
00:41:09,600 --> 00:41:11,220
Why did I faint...

680
00:41:14,090 --> 00:41:15,130
You should tell her.

681
00:41:17,200 --> 00:41:18,600
So you knew!

682
00:41:18,760 --> 00:41:21,190
I asked you the entire afternoon
and you just wouldn't say.

683
00:41:23,160 --> 00:41:25,960
This is too important to Chu Xia.

684
00:41:26,210 --> 00:41:29,010
I can't tell without her permission.

685
00:41:31,720 --> 00:41:32,360
Tell her.

686
00:41:32,440 --> 00:41:33,210
Tell her.

687
00:41:33,860 --> 00:41:35,270
I'm the only one who doesn't know?

688
00:41:40,390 --> 00:41:41,450
Before I tell,

689
00:41:42,710 --> 00:41:45,170
can I remove the clips?

690
00:41:45,360 --> 00:41:46,440
It hurts too much.
